Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒爆發 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的仁兄 請等一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們最好也快點逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一條大蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間就把城堡給毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條蛇有多大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們村之前也被一條很大的蛇襲擊過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條蛇說不定和你遇見的是同一條
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毀掉木葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的回答是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被這些傢伙給騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令弟和叔父大人也一定不希望您這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有綱手大人您的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道您忘了自己的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也非常瞭解您的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然您現在這樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實您…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您清醒點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴 靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不必立刻回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但希望您能在一周內做出決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個禁術需要活祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屆時請自行準備兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 我們就地解決他們把
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和綱手大人聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以解決他們兩個的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 我現在很弱 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道綱手的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 他和綱手大人一樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那件事也...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕見到血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還是沒能克服這個弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液恐懼症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該走了 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手 我很期待你的答覆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還是晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是大蛇幹得好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起就一直急匆匆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 再來一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 您喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 根本就不見蹤影嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑來跑去這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是一點線索也沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先在這裡吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是居酒屋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說幾次啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是個小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 又沒人叫你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼吃些菜就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 那幹嗎非要在這裡吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去拉麵館之類的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報一般都集中在這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會跑到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了 真夠累的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大姐就是綱手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有50歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到一天就遇到兩個三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還真是個老朋友相聚日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是打個招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位大姐竟然就是\N能夠治癒任何傷痛的女忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就開門見山了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子要求你出任第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好好說到這個 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代已經……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代 果然被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大蛇丸干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親耳聽他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大蛇丸干的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他殺了第三代爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我一樣 是三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 三忍不是木葉的忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 他為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼…是九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸 就是殺死火影爺爺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說他是傳說中的三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道他的底細卻放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她繼任第五代火影是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你給我安靜一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管那麼多 閉嘴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定由你出任五代火影了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你的答覆是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你的弟弟和你的男人復活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會把木葉完全摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話似曾相識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我以前追求你的時候說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人不是說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她帶回村子 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替佐助和卡卡西老師療傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻讓她繼任火影 到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被人拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非真要跟大蛇丸作交易嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼激動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能勝任五代火影的只有綱手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在可怕的大戰時期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為木葉的勝利做出了許多貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的戰鬥以及醫療忍術至今無人能敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她還是初代火影的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上她的個人能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人比他更適合第五代火影這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她成為火影 就要回到村子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就像你說的那樣 給他們倆看病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是木葉的高層 顧問們所決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個下忍就不要多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子跟你以前的弟子不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴臭 腦袋笨 長得也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟第四代比 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都相形見絀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是有史以來最具有忍者素質的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:16:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術精湛 思維清晰 人氣又旺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得也跟我一樣帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是第四代也沒活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了村子 連命都搭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命和金錢不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傻瓜才會輕易獻出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爺爺和第二代 志在平定戰亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果他們為了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壯志未酬身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變了 綱手 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你心裡是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你怎麼能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說我也是五十多的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歲月是可以改變一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿飛老師也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一把歲數了還逞強  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影根本就是個廢物 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傻瓜才會做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這裡是酒館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當著我的面侮辱三代爺爺和第四代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是女人我也不放過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要揍扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠膽量 居然當著我的面挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外邊去解決吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我也是三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付下忍 我可不會那麼當真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘搞定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一分鐘 而是一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付你一根手指足以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 放馬過來吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈我的額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你被我打暈前我想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此執著於火影的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要得到火影的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為火影…火影是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 有空擋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般手段估計贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 不如用那招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這招是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒這樣一起喝酒了 綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒懷念過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你又變漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先 你想也別想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你才沒興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都五十多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:22:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有 這樣子讓我想起了以前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初代火影的遺物 召喚死亡的首飾
